## 🎯 What is Agent Lucie?

Agent Lucie is an AI assistant that runs **entirely on your Mac**, without sending any data to the internet. No subscription, no cloud, no dependency on OpenAI or Google.

It can:
- Control your computer via text or voice
- Automatically generate Word documents
- Remember your past conversations
- **Actively protect your system** against malicious files

